4.You are given a number n. You need to generate and print a pattern based on the given value of n.
Platform : GeeksForGeeks
SOURCECODE : class Solution {
    public ArrayList<Integer> printPat(int n) {
       ArrayList<Integer>s=new ArrayList<>();
         for(int i=n;i>=1;i--){
             for(int j=n;j>=1;j--){
                 for(int k=1;k<=i;k++){
                 s.add(j);
                     
                 }
             }
        s.add(-1);  }
        return s;
    }
}
